raw_meta_yaml:
context:
  version: 0.38.0
  python_min: "3.7"

package:
  name: eventlet
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/e/eventlet/eventlet-${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: a5df970a2431526e4973bd5810bb8c41aa4da18baa531aa18799302c24e19510

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: python -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python ${{ python_min }}
    - pip
    - hatch-vcs >=0.3
    - hatchling >=1.12.2
  run:
    - python >=${{ python_min }}
    - greenlet >=1.0
    - dnspython >=1.15.0
    - pyopenssl

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - eventlet
        - eventlet.green
        - eventlet.green.OpenSSL
        - eventlet.green.http
        - eventlet.green.urllib
        - eventlet.greenio
        - eventlet.hubs
        - eventlet.support
      pip_check: true
  - script:
      - python -c "import eventlet"
    requirements:
      run:
        - python ${{ python_min }}

about:
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Highly concurrent networking library
  homepage: http://eventlet.net
  repository: https://github.com/eventlet/eventlet
  documentation: http://eventlet.net

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - synapticarbors
    - anguslees
